name: Minecraft 3D models
tagline: 3D models of Minecraft items.  I plan on using these in animations.
body:
### Welcome to Minecraft 3D models!
This is the page where I will (try) to keep this up to date with what I have uploaded to the repository.  I will also have links to the animations that get made.

### Current Items!
So far what I've made is:
###
Swords : Stone, Iron, Diamond, Gold (Wood coming soon)
